<subSubSection pageId="85" pageNumber="86" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">
(Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 94" captionStartId="F94" captionText="Figure 94. Distribution of Conostegia muriculata." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.67.6703.figure94" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/96452" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">94</figureCitation>
). Endemic to the Caribbean slope of south eastern Costa Rica and northern Panama, 40-1200 m in elevation.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-Zenodo-Dep="974229" doi="10.3897/phytokeys.67.6703.figure94" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/96452" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" start="Figure 94" startId="F94">
